room_title: Escape room "Sherlock's Home" by Chamber Escapes in Miami
room_description: Become a detective and search for answers in this mysterious case. A Jane Doe was found lying in an abandoned London alley. Who is she, and why would someone want to hurt here? Perhaps, she was Watson's or Sherlock's mistress? You have one hour to investigate Sherlock's home and shed light on the case.
